title: High End Modern Home
info: Nestled in the heart of Long Island, this gem boasts top-notch amenities like high-speed Wifi, a fully-equipped kitchen, and access to both the beach and a shimmering pool. Dive into comfort and style, all for an exclusive stay. Rated 4.5 stars by our guests, it's not just a stay; it's an experience.

title: Stone House Estate
info: Discover the charm of the Stone House Estate, where rustic meets elegance. Spread over 4700 sqft, this 2-bedroom residence offers a serene escape in the heart of Upstate New York. With amenities ranging from high-speed Wifi and a gourmet kitchen to a tranquil beach and refreshing pool, every moment here feels like a luxurious retreat. Rated 4.7 stars by our valued guests, it's a touch of paradise, away from the hustle and bustle.

title: Rock Cave Home
info: Dive into the allure of the dessert. Spanning 800 sqft in the serene landscapes of Utah, this 2-bedroom cave property offers a mesmerizing blend of natural beauty and modern comfort.

title: Beach Retreat
info: Kick back and relax in this tranquil, stylish oasis. BRAND NEW landscaped resort-like outdoor space including furnished pool area with hot tub, lounging deck & outdoor shower. Clean, private, with fully-equipped kitchen on Asbury's quiet and friendly northwest.

title: Waterfront Estate
info: Experience the epitome of luxury at the Waterfront Estate. Situated in the scenic landscapes of New Jersey, this expansive estate covers an impressive 4100 sqft with four lavish bedrooms and three modern bathrooms. Revel in the beachfront views, enjoy the refreshing pool, stay connected with high-speed Wifi, and craft gourmet meals in a fully-equipped kitchen. Boasting a perfect 5-star rating, it's an oceanic retreat of unparalleled comfort.

title: Private Beach
info: Experience the pinnacle of luxury at the Waterfront Estate. Located in New Jersey, this beachfront haven offers 3600 sqft of sheer opulence. Two spacious bedrooms and a modern bath ensure you're surrounded by comfort. Wake up to breathtaking beach views, take a dip in the private pool, and enjoy amenities like high-speed Wifi and a gourmet kitchen. With a perfect 5-star rating, this estate defines beachside grandeur.

title: Private Beach Villa
info: Dive into the serene luxury of the Private Beach Villa. Nestled in the heart of New York, this villa spans a generous 2400 sqft, featuring three cozy bedrooms and two pristine bathrooms. Relish direct beach access, surf the web with high-speed Wifi, or cook up a storm in the state-of-the-art kitchen. Rated at 4.4 stars, it's a beach lover's paradise waiting to be explored.

title: Modern Manor
info: Dive into opulence at the Modern Manor, nestled in the heart of New York. Spanning a grand 4500 sqft, this manor is the epitome of modern living with five luxurious bedrooms and four pristine bathrooms. Whether you're taking a dip in the pool, serving aces on the tennis court, breaking a sweat in the gym, or just enjoying the high-speed Wifi and gourmet kitchen, it promises a stay of utmost comfort and style. And, with a flawless 5-star rating, this manor is truly in a class of its own.

title: LakeFront Estate
info: Experience sheer grandeur at the LakeFront Estate, an emblem of luxury set against the serene backdrop of Canada. This sprawling mansion, boasting a vast 6100 sqft, offers six spacious bedrooms and five lavish bathrooms, ensuring an unparalleled stay for its guests. Revel in the breathtaking lakefront views, enjoy a swim in the pool, or feel secure with the state-of-the-art property cameras. With its top-notch amenities, including high-speed Wifi and a gourmet kitchen, and a commendable 4.5-star rating, the LakeFront Estate defines magnificence in every square foot.

title: Historian Palace
info: Step into a world of opulence and history at the Historian Palace, a testament to timeless elegance situated in the heart of Kentucky. With a staggering 7500 sqft of space, this majestic mansion offers eight lavish bedrooms and seven sumptuous bathrooms, making it an ideal retreat for large gatherings or families. Dive into the indoor pool, unwind in the hot tub, or simply traverse the floors with ease using the modern elevator. With impeccable amenities, from high-speed Wifi to a fully-equipped gym, and an outstanding rating of 4.9 stars, the Historian Palace is truly a realm of luxury and comfort.

title: Eco Cottage
info: Nestled amidst the serene landscapes of Colorado, the Eco Cottage offers a harmonious blend of comfort and sustainability. This eco-friendly retreat, spanning 950 sqft, is perfect for those seeking a cozy escape with its two charming bedrooms and a bathroom. Embrace the modern conveniences of life with amenities like high-speed Wifi, state-of-the-art electronics, and HDTV with streaming services. After a day of skiing adventures, unwind on the balcony with breathtaking views or indulge in fun games provided. Rated at a commendable 4.7 stars, the Eco Cottage is your perfect mountain haven.

title: Modern Chefs Kitchen
info: Indulge in culinary delights at the Modern Chef's Kitchen located in the picturesque landscapes of Vermont. This 3,150 sqft luxurious abode boasts three spacious bedrooms and two elegant bathrooms. Designed for the passionate cook, the house features a state-of-the-art chef's kitchen, allowing you to whip up gourmet dishes. After a delightful meal, rejuvenate in the pool, unwind on the balcony with a serene view, or pamper yourself in the hot tub and sauna. With a stellar rating of 4.8 stars, this property promises a lavish stay for those who appreciate the finer things in life.

title: Countryside Manor
info: Escape the urban hustle and immerse yourself in the serene embrace of the Countryside Manor. Nestled in the peaceful terrains of New Jersey, this expansive 6,300 sqft sanctuary offers five plush bedrooms and four luxurious bathrooms. Whether you're taking a refreshing dip in the pool, enjoying the calming garden views, or gathering around the fire pit for a cozy evening, every moment here feels like a retreat. Complete with modern amenities like Wifi, a well-equipped kitchen, and a gym, the manor also offers the convenience of self check-in. Rated at 4.8 stars, this countryside jewel is the epitome of relaxation and luxury.

title: Mediterranean Villa
info: Dive into a tropical paradise with the Mediterranean Villa located in the breathtaking landscapes of Bali. This 1,100 sqft slice of heaven, adorned with two cozy bedrooms and a lavish bathroom, is perfect for those looking to experience the tranquil vibes of the tropics. Recharge by the poolside, feel the sand between your toes at the beach, or simply soak in the mesmerizing views from your private balcony. With top-notch amenities like Wifi and a fully-equipped kitchen, every moment here is curated for your utmost comfort. Boasting a 4.9-star rating, this villa is your dream tropical getaway waiting to be explored.

title: Mirrored Desert Fortress
info: Step into an architectural marvel with the Mirrored Desert Fortress, nestled amidst the vast expanses of Mexico's serene desert landscape. Spanning a spacious 3,100 sqft, this fortress features three well-appointed bedrooms and two luxurious bathrooms, promising a unique blend of comfort and style. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty as you take a dip in your private pool, refresh under the outside shower, or simply relax on the balcony, enjoying the expansive desert views. With amenities like Wifi and a state-of-the-art kitchen, your stay is bound to be as convenient as it is captivating. Rated 4.9 stars, this desert oasis beckons those seeking a one-of-a-kind retreat.

title: Bed & Breakfast
info: Experience the quintessential charm of North Carolina with a stay at our Bed & Breakfast. Spanning a generous 4,700 sqft, this cozy retreat boasts five inviting bedrooms and five well-appointed baths, ensuring utmost comfort for every guest. Wake up to a delicious breakfast spread every morning, a highlight of your stay. The property is equipped with modern amenities including Wifi and a fully-functional kitchen, while the balcony offers a serene spot to relax. Just a short distance from the beach, this B&B, with a rating of 4.6 stars, promises a mix of relaxation and adventure.

title: Lakefront Villa
info: Accommodate up to 10 cars comfortably in the driveway. Immerse yourself in the serene surroundings with lake activities including swimming and late-night fire pits. Feel free to use the kayaks available: two for adults and two for children
